        "created_at": "2018-11-04T05:44:37.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2916162\"><strong>1971 Bruno Giacosa Nebbiolo d\u2019Alba Valmaggiore</strong></a> <em>- Italy, Piedmont, Alba, Nebbiolo d\u2019Alba (11/3/2018)</em><br>\nA beautiful bottle that kept growing in the glass. Gave it a 4 hour decant and it poured out with some leather, truffle and mushroom notes. It sweetened up and become more expansive, offering all sorts of Indian spice and savoury nuance. It had excellent depth and some chew from the structural elements. Length was impressive.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
